f.d:
de nas de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das shAkya thub pa'i mdzod spu nas byang chub sems dpa'i stobs snang ba zhes bya ba'i 'od zer 'khor gyi 'od zer brgya stong grangs med pa dang ldan pa byung ngo; ;
de byung nas phyogs bcu thams cad kyi 'jig rten gyi khams 'byams klas pa thams cad ma lus par snang bar byas nas/ sems can thams cad kyi ngan song gi sdug bsngal thams cad rtse zil bar byas te/ bdud kyi khyim thams cad zil gyis mnan nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor snang bar byas te/ sangs rgyas kyi yul gyi rnam pa bsam gyi mi khyab pa'i mthu bstan nas/ phyogs bcu thams cad kyi 'jig rten gyi khams 'byams klas pa thams cad du de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor du chos bstan pa'i byin gyi rlabs kyis byin du brlabs pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i lus snang bar byas te/ sangs rgyas kyi rnam par 'phrul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa bstan nas steng gi bar snang la 'od zer stug po'i sprin gyi dra ba'i khang pa brtsegs pa chen por byas te 'dug go /de bzhin du sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag gi mdzod spu dag nas kyang / byang chub sems dpa'i 'od snang ba zhes bya ba'i 'od zer 'khor gyi 'od zer grangs med pa dang ldan pa dag byung bar gyur to/ /

byung nas kyang de dag gis phyogs bcu thams cad du 'jig rten gyi khams 'byams klas pa kun tu de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor du chos bstan pa'i byin gyis byin du brlabs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams snang bar byas te/ sangs rgyas kyi rnam par 'phrul ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa bstan nas/ 'jig rten gyi khams mi mjed 'di yang snang bar byas/ bcom ldan 'das shAkya thub pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor 'di yang snang bar byas te/ byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rdo rje'i snying po'i lus kyang snang bar byas nas/ steng gi bar snang la de bzhin du 'od zer stug po'i sprin gyi dra ba'i khang pa brtsegs pa chen por byas te 'khod do/ /

mkhas pa'i spyod pa de 'dra dam pa thos nas/ / lha yi tshogs dang lha yi dbang po kun dga'/ / byang chub sems dpa' 'gro phan brtson pa mang po/ / bde bar gshegs dang rgyal sras rnams la mchod byed/ /
me tog phreng ba rgyal mtshan ba dan yid 'ong / / spos dang phye ma rin chen na bza' rgyan pa/ / dbyig gis spras pa'i gdugs rab khrag khrig du ma/ / phreng ba'i sprin gyi dam pa'i char yang mngon 'bebs/ /
lha yi bu mos yid du 'ong ba'i sgra dbyangs/ / du ma'i sil snyan gar gyi mchog dang ldan byas/ / bde bar gshegs dang rgyal sras mchod pa'i don du/ / thub pa'i yon tan rmad du byung brjod byed; ;

gzhan yang chos tha dad pa yang dag par shes pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mtshan nyid gcig tu khong du chud par bya ba la rab tu 'jug go /don tha dad pa yang dag par shes pas dus dang / dngos po dang / mtshan nyid rnam par phye ba sna tshogs khong du chud par bya ba rab tu shes so/ /
nges pa'i tshig tha dad pa yang dag par shes pas khong du chud pa rnam par phye ba bzhin du bstan pas chos ston to; ;
spobs pa tha dad pa yang dag par shes pas chos kyi tshig re re la yang bskal pa mtha' yas par rgyun mi 'chad par chos ston to/ /
